                <p class="mt-4 text-tanira-gray">Masalah klasik yang terus berulang menghambat potensi pertanian lokal kita.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
                <!-- Problem 1 -->
                <div class="group bg-tanira-cream rounded-2xl overflow-hidden hover:shadow-xl transition duration-300 border border-transparent hover:border-tanira-brown/10 reveal reveal-delay-100">
                    <div class="h-48 overflow-hidden relative">
                        <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1563514227147-6d2ff665a6a0?q=80&w=1471&auto=format&fit=crop" alt="Harga anjlok" class="w-full h-full object-cover group-hover:scale-110 transition duration-500">
                        <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-black/20 group-hover:bg-black/10 transition"></div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="p-8">
                        <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-red-100 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-red-600 mb-4 text-xl">
                            <i class="fa-solid fa-arrow-trend-down"></i>
                        </div>
                        <h4 class="text-xl font-bold text-tanira-dark mb-3">Harga Jatuh Saat Panen</h4>
                        <p class="text-tanira-gray text-sm leading-relaxed">
                            Suplai berlebih dan permainan tengkulak membuat harga jual seringkali di bawah modal tanam.
                        </p>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <!-- Problem 2 -->
                <div class="group bg-tanira-cream rounded-2xl overflow-hidden hover:shadow-xl transition duration-300 border border-transparent hover:border-tanira-brown/10 reveal reveal-delay-200">
                    <div class="h-48 overflow-hidden relative">
                        <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1599930113854-d6d7fd521f10?q=80&w=800&auto=format&fit=crop" alt="Akses pasar terbatas" class="w-full h-full object-cover group-hover:scale-110 transition duration-500">
                        <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-black/20 group-hover:bg-black/10 transition"></div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="p-8">
                        <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-orange-100 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-orange-600 mb-4 text-xl">
                            <i class="fa-solid fa-hand-holding-dollar"></i>
                        </div>
                        <h4 class="text-xl font-bold text-tanira-dark mb-3">Ketergantungan Tengkulak</h4>
                        <p class="text-tanira-gray text-sm leading-relaxed">
                            Rantai distribusi yang panjang memotong keuntungan petani hingga titik terendah.
                        </p>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <!-- Problem 3 -->
                <div class="group bg-tanira-cream rounded-2xl overflow-hidden hover:shadow-xl transition duration-300 border border-transparent hover:border-tanira-brown/10 reveal reveal-delay-300">
                    <div class="h-48 overflow-hidden relative">
                        <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1592419044706-39796d40f98c?q=80&w=800&auto=format&fit=crop" alt="Alat mahal" class="w-full h-full object-cover group-hover:scale-110 transition duration-500">
                        <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-black/20 group-hover:bg-black/10 transition"></div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="p-8">
                        <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-gray-200 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-gray-700 mb-4 text-xl">
                            <i class="fa-solid fa-wrench"></i>
                        </div>
                        <h4 class="text-xl font-bold text-tanira-dark mb-3">Teknologi & Alat Mahal</h4>
                        <p class="text-tanira-gray text-sm leading-relaxed">
                            Sulit mengakses alat modern untuk efisiensi karena biaya beli yang sangat tinggi.
                        </p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Solution / Value Proposition -->
    <section id="solutions" class="py-20 bg-tanira-green/5 relative bg-pattern-leaf">
        <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
            <div class="text-center mb-16 reveal">
                <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-tanira-dark">Solusi Ekosistem TANIRA</h2>
                <p class="mt-4 text-tanira-gray max-w-2xl mx-auto">Kami membangun jembatan digital agar petani bisa bertransaksi dengan adil dan efisien.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-6">
                <!-- Feature 1 -->
                <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-2xl shadow-sm hover:shadow-md transition-all border-b-4 border-tanira-green reveal reveal-delay-100">
                    <div class="w-14 h-14 bg-green-50 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center text-tanira-green text-2xl mb-6">
                        <i class="fa-solid fa-handshake-simple"></i>
                    </div>
                    <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-tanira-dark mb-2">Pre-Order Panen</h3>
                    <p class="text-sm text-tanira-gray">Dapatkan kepastian pembeli dan harga bahkan sebelum benih ditanam.</p>
                </div>

                <!-- Feature 2 -->
                <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-2xl shadow-sm hover:shadow-md transition-all border-b-4 border-tanira-brown reveal reveal-delay-200">
                    <div class="w-14 h-14 bg-amber-50 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center text-tanira-brown text-2xl mb-6">
                        <i class="fa-solid fa-tractor"></i>
                    </div>
                    <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-tanira-dark mb-2">Marketplace Alat</h3>
                    <p class="text-sm text-tanira-gray">Beli atau sewa alat pertanian dari produsen lokal dengan harga transparan.</p>
                </div>

                <!-- Feature 3 -->
                <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-2xl shadow-sm hover:shadow-md transition-all border-b-4 border-tanira-accent reveal reveal-delay-300">
                    <div class="w-14 h-14 bg-yellow-50 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center text-tanira-accent text-2xl mb-6">
                        <i class="fa-solid fa-scale-balanced"></i>
                    </div>
                    <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-tanira-dark mb-2">Harga Referensi</h3>
                    <p class="text-sm text-tanira-gray">Data harga pasar real-time agar petani tidak tertipu spekulan.</p>
                </div>

                <!-- Feature 4 -->
                <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-2xl shadow-sm hover:shadow-md transition-all border-b-4 border-blue-500 reveal reveal-delay-300">
                    <div class="w-14 h-14 bg-blue-50 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center text-blue-600 text-2xl mb-6">
                        <i class="fa-solid fa-robot"></i>
                    </div>
                    <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-tanira-dark mb-2">AI Asisten Tanam</h3>
                    <p class="text-sm text-tanira-gray">Rekomendasi waktu tanam terbaik berdasarkan cuaca dan tren pasar.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- How It Works -->
    <section id="how-it-works" class="py-20 bg-white">
        <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
            <div class="flex flex-col lg:flex-row gap-12 items-center">
                <div class="lg:w-1/2 reveal">
                    <h2 class="text-tanira-green font-bold uppercase tracking-wider mb-2">Langkah Mudah</h2>
                    <h3 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-tanira-dark mb-6">Mulai Transaksi dalam 4 Tahap</h3>
                    <p class="text-tanira-gray mb-8">Tanira menyederhanakan proses rantai pasok yang rumit menjadi langkah sederhana dalam genggaman.</p>
                    
                    <div class="space-y-6">
                        <!-- Step 1 -->
                        <div class="flex gap-4 group">
                            <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-tanira-green text-white flex items-center justify-center font-bold text-lg group-hover:scale-110 transition">1</div>
                            <div>
                                <h4 class="font-bold text-lg text-tanira-dark">Daftarkan Lahan</h4>
                                <p class="text-sm text-tanira-gray">Isi data luas lahan, lokasi, dan komoditas.</p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <!-- Step 2 -->
                        <div class="flex gap-4 group">
                            <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-tanira-cream text-tanira-green border border-tanira-green flex items-center justify-center font-bold text-lg group-hover:bg-tanira-green group-hover:text-white transition">2</div>
                            <div>
                                <h4 class="font-bold text-lg text-tanira-dark">Buat Rencana Tanam</h4>
                                <p class="text-sm text-tanira-gray">Tentukan target panen untuk ditawarkan ke pembeli.</p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <!-- Step 3 -->
                        <div class="flex gap-4 group">
                            <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-tanira-cream text-tanira-green border border-tanira-green flex items-center justify-center font-bold text-lg group-hover:bg-tanira-green group-hover:text-white transition">3</div>
                            <div>
                                <h4 class="font-bold text-lg text-tanira-dark">Terima Pre-Order</h4>
                                <p class="text-sm text-tanira-gray">Pembeli mengajukan penawaran, deal harga di awal.</p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <!-- Step 4 -->
                        <div class="flex gap-4 group">
                            <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-tanira-cream text-tanira-green border border-tanira-green flex items-center justify-center font-bold text-lg group-hover:bg-tanira-green group-hover:text-white transition">4</div>
                            <div>
                                <h4 class="font-bold text-lg text-tanira-dark">Panen & Kirim</h4>
                                <p class="text-sm text-tanira-gray">Pembayaran cair otomatis saat barang diterima.</p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                
                <div class="lg:w-1/2 relative reveal reveal-delay-200">
                    <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-tanira-green/10 rounded-3xl transform rotate-3"></div>
                    <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1605000797499-95a51c5269ae?q=80&w=800&auto=format&fit=crop" alt="Petani menggunakan HP" class="relative rounded-3xl shadow-xl w-full object-cover h-[400px] lg:h-[500px]">
                    <!-- Floating Badge -->
                    <div class="absolute -bottom-6 -left-6 bg-white p-4 rounded-xl shadow-lg flex items-center gap-3 animate-bounce" style="animation-duration: 3s;">
                        <i class="fa-solid fa-check-circle text-green-500 text-3xl"></i>
                        <div>
                            <p class="text-xs text-gray-500">Status Pembayaran</p>
                            <p class="font-bold text-tanira-dark">Dana Cair 100%</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Key Features Highlight -->
    <section class="py-20 bg-tanira-dark text-white">
        <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
            <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-8 text-center divide-y md:divide-y-0 md:divide-x divide-gray-700">
                <div class="p-4 reveal reveal-delay-100">
                    <i class="fa-solid fa-users-viewfinder text-4xl text-tanira-accent mb-4"></i>
                    <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-2">Komunitas Terverifikasi</h3>
                    <p class="text-gray-400 text-sm">Semua petani dan pembeli melewati proses KYC untuk keamanan transaksi.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="p-4 reveal reveal-delay-200">
                    <i class="fa-solid fa-truck-fast text-4xl text-tanira-accent mb-4"></i>
                    <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-2">Logistik Terintegrasi</h3>
                    <p class="text-gray-400 text-sm">Kerjasama dengan penyedia logistik lokal untuk penjemputan hasil panen.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="p-4 reveal reveal-delay-300">
                    <i class="fa-solid fa-leaf text-4xl text-tanira-accent mb-4"></i>
                    <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-2">Sustainable Farming</h3>
                    <p class="text-gray-400 text-sm">Insentif harga untuk petani yang menggunakan metode ramah lingkungan.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Testimonials Section -->
